<i>noun</i>: 포옹 [포ː옹], 포섭 [포ː섭] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>포옹 [포ː옹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hug; holding; embracing</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 품에 안거나 사람끼리 껴안음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of holding someone in one's arms or for two people to embrace each other.</dd><br>
<dd>2. acceptance; understanding</dd><br>
<dd>남을 넓은 마음으로 이해하고 품어 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of understanding and accepting someone with an open mind.</dd><br>
<dt>포섭 [포ː섭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. winning over; embracing</dd><br>
<dd>적이나 상대편을 자기편으로 끌어들임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of luring an enemy or other party to join one's own side.</dd><br>
<dd>2. class inclusion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 개념이 보다 일반적인 개념에 속하는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a certain concept belonging to a more general concept.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>